data.description: Incredible location! This 2 story, 4 sided brick traditional home is on an acre lot in the city of Cartersville. Full unfinished basement. French doors throughout home to bring light and charm, built in shelves add a classic touch to the family room. Large kitchen with breakfast area/screened porch/large deck for entertaining. Formal dining room and a potential separate teen suite with separate stairs from the garage.  All new windows through out the home. Large, level, private yard. No subdivision/no HOA!
